{"tid":1569553,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港黑警資料庫 眾籌提案請求","createTime":"2019-09-14T16:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T15:22:01.000Z","uid":252591,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fb42b840a9f0f0e5d065cfc142f4934a4788a9e7","tid":1569553,"uid":252591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"香港黑警資料庫 眾籌提案請求<br />\n保證一分一毫皆用以宣揚黑警反人類罪行罪證<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">前言</span></ins></strong><br />\n如 7月頭 Admin 所述<br />\n要擊倒港共極權政府 <br />\n(而家已經變左一隻黑/白/黨鐵/CCTVB/中共合體怪物)<br />\n必先擊潰守係陣前既最後一道防線<br />\n而中心思想就係先智取 非必要時不力敵<br />\n<br />\n當然呢條防線係呢三個幾月亦有好大變化<br />\n例如有老豆搵仔既出現 黑警越趨濫暴濫權<br />\n休班警棍隨身 甲由論等<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係黑警 blacker than black<br />\n呢場運動可能一早 die down 左<br />\n<br />\nAdmin 暫時將黑警罪狀分為 33 種 (未來一定更多)<br />\n詳細分類可睇 <a href=\"https://www.hkcpgdb.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcpgdb.com&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=cb8a2cff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcpgdb.com</a><br />\n入面已有過百個 post 羅列罪證<br />\n手頭上既資料應該開到300個 post 以上<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">眾籌提案請求 眾籌資金用以</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 妥善將黑警犯罪資料分類及儲存<br />\n2. 以影片或圖片文宣方式宣揚警渣惡行<br />\n3. 整合黑警片段 盡力支援抗爭者<br />\n4. 展開長期杯葛警渣運動 包括休班警 輔警 休班警 退休警 及辭職警<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為可以甩到身 只要你做過警察 一世就係香港戰犯 <br />\n<br />\n參考呢個 post 加上先前港人港地亦係 youtube 賣過廣告<br />\n<br />\n首個眾籌YOUTUBE廣告！上線了！感謝大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1555632/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1555632/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n相信而家網上文宣宣傳黑警反人類戰爭罪行仍然有好大空間<br />\n至於要籌幾多錢 做到幾多野 相信要睇餸食飯<br />\n希望用一個細水會長流既方式 日日 loop 黑警對市民做過既事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>暫時眾籌 link</ins></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcpgdb.com/donate.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcpgdb.com%2Fdonate.html&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=7881034f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcpgdb.com/donate.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都知道 每一次黑警惡行都可以將運動重撚 並推向高峰 呢個仇我地香港人係唔可以忘記<br />\n<br />\n下一步 admin 會試做黑警犯罪實錄片段 (用黎做廣告文宣)<br />\n無時無刻講比香港市民知 香港市民與垃圾警渣 此仇不共戴天 !"},{"pid":"be287666854174a345d4cc32b163901fbfdc3e2d","tid":1569553,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"690267437b2ff7000443c678b38b84736fc3518a","tid":1569553,"uid":81449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:06:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d12f759cb47ae08c3d3911a16eedc9b3065ece6","tid":1569553,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1921ed6deff921980058c90b40921f06c871829","tid":1569553,"uid":134583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"支持 <br />\n推"},{"pid":"ceae7ddf3c5dd037666bdc0a71a001bc9ce53313","tid":1569553,"uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:08:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n黑警死全家"},{"pid":"8c563ed1c5c0ef8c11e9f1ef114739f2074c3a4b","tid":1569553,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"Set左每月捐款了<br />\n加油 依個資料庫好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132a8740c06d9e61c9b771c6504344d4dffafb06","tid":1569553,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"da37709119cff7b873c00dc37ecb7046e967f589","tid":1569553,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:14:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e43f8cc747bae26b0fdd88fbfdf2f8cd33babec","tid":1569553,"uid":65753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38815e9a72213bdbe6d2eaa7d5a7886891159115","tid":1569553,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95766a504d43ac2f727ea90dda86fd80a60adc35","tid":1569553,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:19:45.000Z","msg":"樓主一個人定團隊?"},{"pid":"71b3aa1a17bf18e24efaa02cd7032159105e1150","tid":1569553,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:20:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"3cb771205b6fe2c99ca10e294fa642e7752f0eea","tid":1569553,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"個眾籌網簡體字咩玩法<br />\n咩平台黎<br />\n<br />\n會否用返正常平台<br />\n同埋可否解釋多少少d 錢點用"},{"pid":"ead9c084bcd3c281d9ace1f52594b8351378e5ec","tid":1569553,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cb771205b6fe2c99ca10e294fa642e7752f0eea","tid":1569553,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"個眾籌網簡體字咩玩法<br />\n咩平台黎<br />\n<br />\n會否用返正常平台<br />\n同埋可否解釋多少少d 錢點用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n我信樓主的<br />\n<br />\n但個眾籌網有d流.."},{"pid